caption:
hello friends, it’s time for commissions again! I’m trying to save some money but I also have fuel/phone/etc expenses that’re gonna eat into what little money I earn lol 

So! 

Headshots

sketch: $15 USD
Lineart + flats- $22 USD
Colour/shading - $25 USD

Mid Body

sketch: $25 USD
Lineart+Flats - $32 USD
Colour/shading - $35 USD

Illustration: 

Rough sketch: $40USD
Flat coloured sketch - $50 USD
Full Colour Illustration: $80+ USD (calculated on time spent)
Additional Character: $20USD

MUSIC
Samples: Found here

$1 USD per second of music, up to 30 seconds with a minimum of 15. 
I’ll need to know what sort of music you’re into, and at the moment it’s purely instrumental with non-specific choral music because I can’t sing for shit. 

CONTACT

either at 

email : monstercade@gmail.com

tumblr ask 

twitter

website

All work will be invoiced, and you’ll receive an invoice when I’m halfway through your work, along with samples so we can make some changes if need be.

Ko-fi
